name: Mother
description: The mother experienced battles that her innocent children are too small to understand, in which they are about to receive a gift that cost her dearly but that will last for eternity in their hearts. The yellow rose represents his legacy of the experiences lived in the adult world; where every act is a risk, and a struggle to live every day. Housed in a cave filled with red roses that is the love and life force donated during their lives to them.
